            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-indigo-300 mb-4 flex items-center">
              <i class="fas fa-balance-scale mr-2"></i> Columnar vs. Standard Time Series
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">
              SoliDB offers two distinct approaches for handling time-based data. Choosing the right one depends on your ingestion and query patterns.
            </p>
            
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-white/10">
